5. When the price of Bitcoin is high Tether Foundation sells Bitcoin for Tether on Bitfinex and withdraws Tether from the market. This reduces the supply and price of Bitcoin.

4.When the price of Bitcoin is low Tether Foundation issues new tokens of Tether without having real coverage in dollars. It sends these tokens to Bitfinex and uses them to buy Bitcoin at low prices. This increases the demand and price of Bitcoin.
